Class CypherWalker

  • java.lang.Object
    • parsing_lexing.CypherBaseListener
      • translator.CypherWalker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener, CypherListener 

    public class CypherWalker
extends CypherBaseListener
    Class that walks the parse tree of the Cypher input, as parsed by the ANTLRv4 tool. This class records important information about the query.
